 office with natural lighting and workers","category":"Office"},{"src":"/catalogs/QX-0/gallery/office-arrangement.jpg","alt":"QX executive desk in private office with monitor arm setup","category":"Office"},{"src":"/catalogs/QX-0/gallery/desk-detail.jpg","alt":"Close-up of QX desk edge showing oak grain and steel joint detail","category":"Detail"},{"src":"/catalogs/QX-0/gallery/office-lifestyle.jpg","alt":"Modern conference room with QX conference table and chairs","category":"Office"}]},"catalogId":"QX-0"}],"$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a"]}]]}]
